{"word":"G4323 - προσανατίθημι - prosanatíthēmi - pros-an-at-ith'-ay-mee - In conference add","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσανατίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosanatíthēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-an-at-ith'-ay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">In conference add</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - யோசனை பண்ணு, போதி"},{"paragraph":"1. to lay upon in addition"},{"paragraph":"2. to add from one's store"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G394 - ἀνατίθεμαι - anatíthemai - an-at-ith'-em-ahee/394\">G394</a>; to <i>lay up in addition</i>, that is, (middle voice and figuratively) to <i>impart</i> or (by implication) to <i>consult:</i> - in conference add, confer.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2652/2652\">G2652</a>, <a href=\"#/G2653/2653\">G2653</a>, <a href=\"#/G331/331\">G331</a>, <a href=\"#/G332/332\">G332</a>, <a href=\"#/G334/334\">G334</a>, <a href=\"#/G394/394\">G394</a>, <a href=\"#/G4323/4323\">G4323</a>"}]}